423
00:30:43,840 --> 00:30:47,100
 kongruentnu poruku, jasnu poruku,

424
00:30:47,100 --> 00:30:48,400
 usklađenu poruku,

425
00:30:48,400 --> 00:30:50,820
 a ne da nešto mama dozvoljava,

426
00:30:50,820 --> 00:30:51,480
