456
00:32:01,280 --> 00:32:03,520
 i izuzetno je važno

457
00:32:03,520 --> 00:32:04,800
 što mali broj ljudi zna

458
00:32:04,800 --> 00:32:07,080
 što ja zapravo želim od partnera,

459
00:32:07,080 --> 00:32:08,220
