00:35:01,300 --> 00:35:02,800
 Naravno, mislim,

544
00:35:02,800 --> 00:35:05,340
 to nije kupoprodavni proces.

545
00:35:05,340 --> 00:35:07,480
 Znači, ljubav je prekrasna,

546
00:35:07,480 --> 00:35:10,580
 ali ljubav je, kako bi rekao,

547
00:35:10,580 --> 00:35:12,100
