 Nije slučajno, Delfima pisalo u Grčkoj, spozne sebe samog.

806
00:44:08,780 --> 00:44:10,600
 Stoga ljudi kod mene ulazi u program.

807
00:44:10,600 --> 00:44:12,340
 Zapravo kao u mini studiji,

808
00:44:12,340 --> 00:44:14,680
 gdje imaju priliku spoznat sebe,

809
00:44:14,680 --> 00:44:16,960
 obuznat sebe i oplemenit sebe.

810
00:44:16,960 --> 00:44:17,820
 Kako to radite?

811
00:44:17,820 --> 00:44:20,260
 Pa, znači, prva ostana stvar,

812
00:44:20,260 --> 00:44:23,620
 znači, napravimo jedan strukturiran intervju

813
00:44:23,620 --> 00:44:26,560
 i na temelju niza aspekate.

814
00:44:26,560 --> 00:44:28,700
 Ja mogu, kao što sam i vamo pokazao prije,

815
00:44:28,700 --> 00:44:32,620
 znači, jako brzo mogu skinuti te obrazce.

816
00:44:32,620 --> 00:44:34,440
 I onda je cilj...

817
00:44:34,440 --> 00:44:37,360
 Moram odmah reći da ste pogodili 99%.

818
00:44:37,360 --> 00:44:41,320
 Ono, sad, ono, kad kažete pogađanje...

819
00:44:41,320 --> 00:44:42,400
 Pogodili, definirali.

820
00:44:42,400 --> 00:44:43,420
 Dobro, dobro mi je.

821
00:44:43,420 --> 00:44:45,180
 Zato što mi jedan kolega je rekao,

822
00:44:45,180 --> 00:44:46,640
 znaš što, treba bi se baviti gatenjem,

823
00:44:46,640 --> 00:44:47,600
 više bi zaradio.

824
00:44:47,600 --> 00:44:47,900
 Eto.

825
00:44:47,900 --> 00:44:50,000
 Ali, znači, nema vize sa pogađanjem,

826
00:44:50,000 --> 00:44:52,080
 znači, ili znaš nešto, ili ne znaš nešto.

827
00:44:52,080 --> 00:44:58,660
 Suštinski cilj je zapravo približiti pomoći osobi

828
00:44:58,660 --> 00:44:59,700
 da osvijesti sebe.

829
00:44:59,700 --> 00:45:02,460
 Da osvijesti zašto misli to što misli,

830
00:45:02,460 --> 00:45:04,100
 zašto osjeća to što osjeća,

831
00:45:04,100 --> 00:45:08,000
 zašto tako reagira i ponaša se prema sebi i drugima.

832
00:45:08,000 --> 00:45:09,660
 Jako mi je bitno...

833
00:45:09,660 --> 00:45:11,620
 Znači, ljudi u tom programu,

834
00:45:11,620 --> 00:45:13,520
 projem to napišem, dam im smjernice,

835
00:45:14,220 --> 00:45:19,940
 i onda oni zajedno sa mnom rade, rade vježbe i kako bi rekao,

836
00:45:19,940 --> 00:45:24,980
 pogotovo je to važno sa djecom i jako puno rojetelja dolazi da ih naučim kako,

837
00:45:24,980 --> 00:45:30,060
 ne generalno sa djecom, nego sa svojim djetetom.

838
00:45:30,600 --> 00:45:32,340
 Koji su njegove potencijali,

839
00:45:32,340 --> 00:45:34,940
 na koji način se nose sa stresom,

840
00:45:34,940 --> 00:45:37,920
 kako se slagati sa svojim djetetom,

841
00:45:37,920 --> 00:45:42,260
 u kojom smjeru ga razvijati,

842
00:45:42,260 --> 00:45:43,800
 koje su mu slabosti.

843
00:45:45,060 --> 00:45:46,780
 Jako, jako bitno,

844
00:45:46,780 --> 00:45:49,340
 jer nismo svijestni da se ne razumijemo.

845
00:45:49,340 --> 00:45:50,480
 I obično ljudima kažem,

846
00:45:50,480 --> 00:45:52,620
 svaki put kad ste u kontaktu s nekim,

847
00:45:52,620 --> 00:45:56,260
 da li djetetom, partnerom, kolegom, prijateljem,

848
00:45:56,260 --> 00:45:57,880
 mi pristupamo drugom računom.

849
00:45:57,880 --> 00:46:03,400
 I ne razmišljati da mislimo isto,

850
00:46:03,400 --> 00:46:06,140
 nego uvijek razgovarati s tim da se razumijemo.

851
00:46:06,140 --> 00:46:08,740
 Znači, to je prvi preduvjet da se ne razočaramo.

852
00:46:08,740 --> 00:46:09,740
 Tako, bravo.

853
00:46:09,740 --> 00:46:14,100
 Svati da nisu svi kao ti.

854
00:46:14,420 --> 00:46:17,460
 I da ne misle isto, ne osjećaju isto.

855
00:46:17,460 --> 00:46:20,700
 Generalno, kad bi kao društvo više razumijeli,

856
00:46:20,700 --> 00:46:22,020
 poštivali različitost,

857
00:46:22,020 --> 00:46:23,480
 bilo bi to puno kvalitetno.

858
00:46:23,480 --> 00:46:25,460
 A što je sa onima koji se ne mogu s tim pomiriti,

859
00:46:25,460 --> 00:46:29,220
 pa kažu, ali to baš mora biti onako kako ja hoću.

860
00:46:29,220 --> 00:46:31,320
 Pa da ima dođen tip karaktera,

861
00:46:31,320 --> 00:46:33,620
 koji je vrlo originan i jednostavno,

862
00:46:33,620 --> 00:46:35,360
 oni znaju šta je ispravno.

863
00:46:35,360 --> 00:46:37,720
 To su oni snimači ratnih filmova?

864
00:46:37,720 --> 00:46:38,980
 Ne, nisu.

865
00:46:38,980 --> 00:46:39,780
 Nisu, ok.

866
00:46:39,780 --> 00:46:42,700
 To su, ajmo reći, ljudi koji su skloni perfekcionizmu,

867
00:46:42,840 --> 00:46:45,300
 koji imaju izjedno visoke standarde u sebi.

868
00:46:45,300 --> 00:46:46,500
 Obično su tehničke struke.

869
00:46:46,500 --> 00:46:48,700
 Znači oni točno znaju što je ispravno.

870
00:46:50,400 --> 00:46:58,120
 Međutim, kako bi to rekao, što si rigidniji, ok.

871
00:46:58,120 --> 00:47:00,240
 To u principu, to je sve interesantno.

872
00:47:00,240 --> 00:47:03,000
 Mislim, mi smo mogli pričati puno o tome,

873
00:47:03,000 --> 00:47:06,860
 ali recimo, koja razlika mi će biti prilagodljiv i fleksibilan?

874
00:47:06,860 --> 00:47:08,580
 Objasnite mi.

875
00:47:08,580 --> 00:47:14,440
 Prilagodljen, znači vrlo često korespondira sa biti indoktriniran.

876
00:47:14,440 --> 00:47:18,320
 Daću primjer, recimo, ako ja odlučim, a nemam veze s tim,

877
00:47:18,320 --> 00:47:20,540
 recimo, na putu sam i želim ući u neku džamiju.

878
00:47:20,540 --> 00:47:22,620
 Ja nisam musliman.

879
00:47:22,620 --> 00:47:25,040
 Ali, zanimav je vidjeti kako to izgleda.

880
00:47:25,040 --> 00:47:27,060
 Pa nekak je kulturno pitaš, prije što uđeš,

881
00:47:27,060 --> 00:47:29,280
 kako bi se trebao obući, što je prikladno što ne prikladno,

882
00:47:29,280 --> 00:47:30,540
 kako bi se trebao ponašati.

883
00:47:30,540 --> 00:47:33,340
 Ušao sam unutra, razgledao sam to sve skupa,

884
00:47:33,340 --> 00:47:35,160
 ispoštivao sam različitosti,

885
00:47:35,160 --> 00:47:37,320
 zašto sam van, skinuo sam se, ja sam ponovo svoj.

886
00:47:37,440 --> 00:47:39,520
 Znači, ja sam bio fleksibilan.

887
00:47:39,520 --> 00:47:41,060
 Ušao sam, kužemo,

888
00:47:41,060 --> 00:47:43,260
 međutim, ostao sam svoj.

889
00:47:43,260 --> 00:47:44,880
 Biti plagodljiv je vrlo često

890
00:47:44,880 --> 00:47:47,020
 direktno vezan za indoktrinaciju.

891
00:47:47,020 --> 00:47:49,160
 I nastavno, njihovi stavovi postoje moji stavovi.

892
00:47:49,160 --> 00:47:51,340
 Zašto sam van, više nisam svoj.

893
00:47:51,340 --> 00:47:53,320
 Vrlo često to problem je

894
00:47:53,320 --> 00:47:54,580
 u odnosu, u vezama,

895
00:47:54,580 --> 00:47:56,680
 gdje zapravo dvoje ljudi,

896
00:47:56,680 --> 00:47:58,600
 da, dijele taj mi osjećaj,

897
00:47:58,600 --> 00:48:00,900
 ali ja ostajem ja, vi ostajete vi,

898
00:48:00,900 --> 00:48:02,380
 ali mi smo zajedno.

899
00:48:02,380 --> 00:48:04,760
 Međutim, kad se počnemo stapati u nešto,

900
00:48:04,760 --> 00:48:06,840
 zapravo gubimo vlastit identitet.

901
00:48:06,840 --> 00:48:09,040
 Znači, kad počnemo misliti tuđim mozgom.

902
00:48:09,040 --> 00:48:10,580
 Preprilagodljivost, dajmo reći.

903
00:48:10,580 --> 00:48:13,880
 I to uvijek rezultira katastrofom.

904
00:48:13,880 --> 00:48:15,640
 Pa mislim, uvijek.

905
00:48:15,640 --> 00:48:17,280
 A tamo je često.

906
00:48:17,280 --> 00:48:17,980
 Jel da?

907
00:48:17,980 --> 00:48:18,300
 Da.

908
00:48:18,300 --> 00:48:21,880
 Što ako jedan od partnera ima neku ovisnost?

909
00:48:21,880 --> 00:48:23,280
 Naprimjer, ne znam, kockanje,

910
00:48:23,280 --> 00:48:24,980
 alkohol, droga.

911
00:48:24,980 --> 00:48:26,460
 Da, jako interesantno.

912
00:48:26,460 --> 00:48:27,960
 Suštinski svi smo ovisni.

913
00:48:27,960 --> 00:48:29,640
 Da.

914
00:48:29,640 --> 00:48:31,040
 Zapravo.

915
00:48:31,040 --> 00:48:32,520
 Kad kaže da smo ovisni,

916
00:48:33,060 --> 00:48:35,420
 o nekoj drogi.

917
00:48:35,420 --> 00:48:37,460
 Zapravo, droga je substitut.

918
00:48:37,460 --> 00:48:38,920
 Mi nismo ovisni o drogi.

919
00:48:38,920 --> 00:48:40,880
 Mi smo ovisni o emociji koje ta droga zaziva.

920
00:48:40,880 --> 00:48:41,560
 Kod nam ona daje.

921
00:48:41,560 --> 00:48:42,320
 Da.

922
00:48:42,320 --> 00:48:47,780
 Znači, svatko, netko može biti ovisan o dobroti.

923
00:48:47,780 --> 00:48:49,000
 Jednostavno, moram raditi.

924
00:48:49,000 --> 00:48:51,480
 Znači, kad god je nešto podmorati, kompulzivno,

925
00:48:51,480 --> 00:48:52,860
 e pa to je ovisnost.

926
00:48:52,860 --> 00:48:55,400
 Znači, i rad može biti ovisnost.

927
00:48:56,820 --> 00:48:57,340
 Uspjeh.

928
00:48:57,340 --> 00:48:57,980
 Aha.

929
00:48:57,980 --> 00:48:58,900
 U redu.

930
00:48:58,900 --> 00:49:00,560
 Znači, neki se pikaju sa uspjehom.

931
00:49:00,560 --> 00:49:03,980
 Neki se pikaju sa srećom, pa su hedonisti.

932
00:49:03,980 --> 00:49:05,960
 Neki se pikaju sa moći.

933
00:49:05,960 --> 00:49:08,340
 Neki se pikaju sa strahom.

934
00:49:08,340 --> 00:49:10,240
 Neki se pikaju sa tugom.

935
00:49:11,300 --> 00:49:12,860
 Znači, toka što smo pričali malo prije,

936
00:49:12,860 --> 00:49:15,120
 zapravo Šekspir rekao da živo teatora,

937
00:49:15,120 --> 00:49:17,860
 a mi samo glumci u tom životnom teatru.

938
00:49:17,860 --> 00:49:20,000
 Ja kažem, teatru naših roditelja.

939
00:49:20,000 --> 00:49:22,540
 I onda, svatko od nas, to je bilo zgodno,

940
00:49:22,540 --> 00:49:25,980
 znači, međugledatelji pitaju,

941
00:49:25,980 --> 00:49:27,820
 kad bi došlo, to smo bili spominjali,

942
00:49:27,820 --> 00:49:31,240
 znači, neki poznati redatelji snimeo film

943
00:49:31,240 --> 00:49:34,740
 o vašem životu, kojeg žanra bi bio taj film.

944
00:49:34,740 --> 00:49:36,720
 Znači, neki snimaju drame,

945
00:49:36,720 --> 00:49:38,900
 naravno je skupljato u tugu,

946
00:49:38,900 --> 00:49:40,060
 neko snima trilere.

947
00:49:40,440 --> 00:49:42,260
 Ja hoću reći, jako je bitno osvijestiti

948
00:49:42,260 --> 00:49:44,400
 i, ajmo reći, u konačnici,

949
00:49:44,400 --> 00:49:45,640
 pre sad biti glumac

950
00:49:45,640 --> 00:49:47,980
 i postati scenarista, redatelji,

951
00:49:47,980 --> 00:49:49,180
 producent svog života.

952
00:49:49,180 --> 00:49:51,300
 A taj život bi trebao nositi

953
00:49:51,300 --> 00:49:54,020
 nekako ime sreća.

954
00:49:54,020 --> 00:49:56,100
 I sad, sreću svatko doživljava

955
00:49:56,100 --> 00:49:57,160
 na svoj način.

956
00:49:57,160 --> 00:49:58,780
 Ne znam da se čovjek osjeća

957
00:49:58,780 --> 00:49:59,980
 da ima taj unutarnji mir,

958
00:49:59,980 --> 00:50:01,300
 da ima unutarnji balans,

959
00:50:01,300 --> 00:50:02,460
 da se osjeća ispunjen.

960
00:50:02,460 --> 00:50:03,780
 Ne je nužno sreća.

961
00:50:03,780 --> 00:50:05,420
 Zadovoljstvo je puno bolja stvar.

962
00:50:05,420 --> 00:50:07,520
 Što bi onda bila formula

963
00:50:07,520 --> 00:50:09,020
 za sreću za svakog od nas?

964
00:50:09,020 --> 00:50:10,520
 Znam da to sad zvuči

965
00:50:10,520 --> 00:50:12,840
 onako bezveze na postavljeno pitanje.

966
00:50:12,840 --> 00:50:14,140
 Hvala je pisao pjesme o tome

967
00:50:14,140 --> 00:50:15,120
 koji je puno sreće.

968
00:50:15,120 --> 00:50:17,800
 Mislim, svatko sreću

969
00:50:17,800 --> 00:50:18,940
 definira drugačije.

970
00:50:18,940 --> 00:50:22,960
 Je jedna od velikih stvari

971
00:50:22,960 --> 00:50:24,280
 koje treba naučiti

972
00:50:24,280 --> 00:50:25,460
 da ono što tražimo izvana

973
00:50:25,460 --> 00:50:26,540
 trebamo naći u sebi.

974
00:50:26,540 --> 00:50:28,340
 Oni koji ganje uspjeh

975
00:50:28,340 --> 00:50:29,940
 zapravo žele biti

976
00:50:29,940 --> 00:50:30,760
 i osjećati se vrijedni,

977
00:50:30,760 --> 00:50:31,600
 ponosni na sebi,

978
00:50:31,600 --> 00:50:32,640
 a zapravo treba shvatiti

979
00:50:32,640 --> 00:50:33,760
 da oni jesu takvi

980
00:50:33,760 --> 00:50:35,240
 samim tim što postoje.

981
00:50:35,240 --> 00:50:37,060
 Da oni koji traži dobrotu,

982
00:50:37,060 --> 00:50:38,160
 raditi dobre stvari,

983
00:50:38,160 --> 00:50:39,840
 da zapravo treba prihvatiti

984
00:50:39,840 --> 00:50:40,900
 da oni jesu dobri ljudi,

985
00:50:40,980 --> 00:50:42,780
 da ne moraju dokazivati dobrotu.

986
00:50:42,780 --> 00:50:45,540
 Da ljudi koji ganjaju sreću

987
00:50:45,540 --> 00:50:46,780
 da trebaju shvatiti

988
00:50:46,780 --> 00:50:48,820
 da oni jesu sreća.

989
00:50:48,820 --> 00:50:50,380
 Da nemoju to tražiti izvana.

990
00:50:50,380 --> 00:50:53,280
 A to je zapravo ono

991
00:50:53,280 --> 00:50:54,160
 čim se ja bavim.

992
00:50:54,160 --> 00:50:56,140
 Moj posao je da identificiram,

993
00:50:56,140 --> 00:50:57,200
 ajmo reći,

994
00:50:57,200 --> 00:50:58,180
 software koji imate,

995
00:50:58,180 --> 00:50:59,300
 da ga upgradeamo

996
00:50:59,300 --> 00:51:00,940
 i da zapravo budete

997
00:51:00,940 --> 00:51:02,440
 puno bolja verzija sebe.

998
00:51:02,440 --> 00:51:03,880
 Ne samo za sebe,

999
00:51:03,880 --> 00:51:05,060
 nego i za partnera,

1000
00:51:05,060 --> 00:51:05,800
 za djecu,

1001
00:51:05,800 --> 00:51:07,200
 za svijet oko nas.

1002
00:51:07,200 --> 00:51:10,020
 I što onda sad danas

1003
00:51:10,020 --> 00:51:11,240
 kad naši gledatelji

1004
00:51:11,240 --> 00:51:12,920
 ovo sad pogledaju,

1005
00:51:12,920 --> 00:51:13,620
 poslušaju,

1006
00:51:13,620 --> 00:51:14,260
 promisle,

1007
00:51:14,260 --> 00:51:15,500
 pitaju se

1008
00:51:15,500 --> 00:51:17,020
 koji film ja snimam,

1009
00:51:17,020 --> 00:51:18,800
 što ćemo im na kraju reći?

1010
00:51:18,800 --> 00:51:20,560
 Ja bih rekao ovako,

1011
00:51:20,560 --> 00:51:21,040
 gledajte,

1012
00:51:21,040 --> 00:51:21,860
 znači,

1013
00:51:21,860 --> 00:51:22,540
 nažalost,

1014
00:51:22,540 --> 00:51:24,080
 ljudi dolaze

1015
00:51:24,080 --> 00:51:25,580
 već kada je kasno,

1016
00:51:25,580 --> 00:51:27,340
 kada je već razvod nastupio,

1017
00:51:27,340 --> 00:51:28,380
 kada su toliko

1018
00:51:28,380 --> 00:51:30,000
 tuđeni jedni od drugoga,

1019
00:51:30,000 --> 00:51:30,900
 kada je,

1020
00:51:30,900 --> 00:51:32,020
 ajmo reći,

1021
00:51:33,220 --> 00:51:34,980
 jako narušen odnos sa dijeti,

1022
00:51:34,980 --> 00:51:36,180
 to imali se dijeti ponašano

1023
00:51:36,180 --> 00:51:37,320
 devijantan način,

1024
00:51:37,320 --> 00:51:40,240
 ili kad se nas bole,

1025
00:51:40,240 --> 00:51:40,700
 znači,

1026
00:51:40,700 --> 00:51:42,600
 puno kvalitetnije

1027
00:51:42,600 --> 00:51:44,560
 prevenirati stvari,

1028
00:51:44,560 --> 00:51:45,080
 znači,

1029
00:51:45,080 --> 00:51:47,220
 čisto informirati se,

1030
00:51:47,220 --> 00:51:50,220
 možda biti dovoljno otvoren

1031
00:51:50,220 --> 00:51:51,960
 i čuti neke stvari,

1032
00:51:51,960 --> 00:51:53,320
 preispitati neke stvari.

1033
00:51:53,700 --> 00:51:54,420
 i to je interesanto,

1034
00:51:54,420 --> 00:51:56,580
 kada država nije definirala

1035
00:51:56,580 --> 00:51:57,340
 zakonski,

1036
00:51:57,340 --> 00:51:58,900
 da mora umišći na tehnički pregled,

1037
00:51:58,900 --> 00:52:01,040
 koliko ljudi bi uopće išlo s autom.

1038
00:52:01,040 --> 00:52:01,680
 Na tehnički.

1039
00:52:01,680 --> 00:52:03,900
 Vozli bi ga dok se ne raspadne,

1040
00:52:03,900 --> 00:52:05,080
 tek onda nešto.

1041
00:52:05,080 --> 00:52:06,100
 Ali mislim,

1042
00:52:06,100 --> 00:52:07,680
 vrlo je slična analogija.

1043
00:52:07,680 --> 00:52:08,000
 Znači,

1044
00:52:08,000 --> 00:52:10,640
 ne želiš dovesti u riziki sebe

1045
00:52:10,640 --> 00:52:11,340
 i druge ljude

1046
00:52:11,340 --> 00:52:12,560
 vozići loš auto.

1047
00:52:12,560 --> 00:52:13,940
 Pa tako i ovo.

1048
00:52:13,940 --> 00:52:16,700
 Imam kolegu Zubara,

1049
00:52:16,700 --> 00:52:17,820
 on isto tako kaže,

1050
00:52:17,820 --> 00:52:18,620
 kod njega dođu

1051
00:52:18,620 --> 00:52:19,180
 kad ti već,

1052
00:52:19,180 --> 00:52:20,740
 da ne vijelim,

1053
00:52:20,740 --> 00:52:21,920
 pa ona se pita,

1054
00:52:21,980 --> 00:52:23,240
 zašto ne dođu čisto na pregled,

1055
00:52:23,240 --> 00:52:23,540
 da vide,

1056
00:52:23,540 --> 00:52:25,320
 pa mogu prevenirati neke stvari.

1057
00:52:25,320 --> 00:52:26,120
 Ovo je namljeno,

1058
00:52:26,120 --> 00:52:27,220
 koji mi manje će i koštiti.

1059
00:52:27,220 --> 00:52:29,380
 Ali kod auta

1060
00:52:29,380 --> 00:52:30,720
 neke stvari možeš zamijeniti

1061
00:52:30,720 --> 00:52:32,240
 kada je u pitanju

1062
00:52:32,240 --> 00:52:34,360
 neke stvari,

1063
00:52:34,360 --> 00:52:35,400
 jednostavno,

1064
00:52:35,400 --> 00:52:36,080
 kada izgubiš,

1065
00:52:36,080 --> 00:52:36,700
 izgubio si

1066
00:52:36,700 --> 00:52:38,260
 i ne možeš...

1067
00:52:38,260 --> 00:52:39,360
 Znači, nema povratka.

1068
00:52:39,360 --> 00:52:39,900
 Da,

1069
00:52:39,900 --> 00:52:41,360
 i onda ti je žao zbog toga.

1070
00:52:41,360 --> 00:52:42,600
 Evo,

1071
00:52:42,600 --> 00:52:43,460
 još jedno pitanje

1072
00:52:43,460 --> 00:52:44,280
 odmah za kraj,

1073
00:52:44,280 --> 00:52:46,060
 to sam vam nešto najavila.

1074
00:52:46,060 --> 00:52:47,140
 Cijelo vrijeme

1075
00:52:47,140 --> 00:52:49,280
 užasno smo ispolitizirana nacija.

1076
00:52:49,700 --> 00:52:50,940
 Sad vas neću pitati

1077
00:52:50,940 --> 00:52:52,220
 dajte mi nešto negativno,

1078
00:52:52,220 --> 00:52:53,120
 nego recite mi

1079
00:52:53,120 --> 00:52:54,760
 jednu dobru stvar

1080
00:52:54,760 --> 00:52:55,960
 u karakteru

1081
00:52:55,960 --> 00:52:56,760
 kod premijera,

1082
00:52:56,760 --> 00:52:57,760
 a jednu dobru

1083
00:52:57,760 --> 00:52:58,700
 kod predsjednika.

1084
00:52:58,700 --> 00:53:01,300
 Pozitivno.

1085
00:53:01,300 --> 00:53:02,780
 Oba dvoje su vođe.

1086
00:53:02,780 --> 00:53:04,300
 Oba dvoje vole

1087
00:53:04,300 --> 00:53:05,860
 moć i kontrolu.

1088
00:53:05,860 --> 00:53:07,160
 Oba dvoje su jake.

1089
00:53:07,160 --> 00:53:08,980
 Međutim,

1090
00:53:08,980 --> 00:53:11,100
 kako bi to rekao...

1091
00:53:11,100 --> 00:53:12,080
 Bićemo pozitivni,

1092
00:53:12,080 --> 00:53:12,620
 profesor.

1093
00:53:12,620 --> 00:53:13,360
 Da, znači,

1094
00:53:13,360 --> 00:53:18,440
 gospodin Andri Prenković,

1095
00:53:18,440 --> 00:53:19,600
 on ima tu,

1096
00:53:19,600 --> 00:53:21,340
 kad bi sad izdvojao nešto

1097
00:53:21,340 --> 00:53:22,360
 što me je jaka strana,

1098
00:53:22,360 --> 00:53:23,800
 ima tu diplomatsku crtu.

1099
00:53:23,800 --> 00:53:25,440
 I on je odlično diplomat.

1100
00:53:26,120 --> 00:53:26,920
 Koliko si rekao

1101
00:53:26,920 --> 00:53:27,700
 to sviđalo, ne ne.

1102
00:53:27,700 --> 00:53:31,080
 A dok je ono što je

1103
00:53:31,080 --> 00:53:33,500
 sigurno kod Milanovića

1104
00:53:33,500 --> 00:53:34,740
 dobra strana,

1105
00:53:34,740 --> 00:53:35,740
 što je prokleto

1106
00:53:35,740 --> 00:53:37,600
 autentičan i direktan.

1107
00:53:37,600 --> 00:53:39,820
 Neki će to nazvat

1108
00:53:39,820 --> 00:53:40,620
 drugim imenom,

1109
00:53:40,620 --> 00:53:41,400
 ali da,

1110
00:53:41,400 --> 00:53:42,980
 kod njega to što zna što je misli.

1111
00:53:42,980 --> 00:53:44,560
 Tako da,

1112
00:53:44,560 --> 00:53:46,220
 kako bi rekao,

1113
00:53:46,220 --> 00:53:48,260
 svatko od nas ima...

1114
00:53:48,260 --> 00:53:49,500
 To je interesantno.

1115
00:53:49,500 --> 00:53:50,480
 Nije poanta.

1116
00:53:50,480 --> 00:53:51,680
 To je netko u nogometu.

1117
00:53:51,680 --> 00:53:53,380
 Znači, netko je za napad,

1118
00:53:53,380 --> 00:53:54,380
 netko je za obranu.

1119
00:53:54,380 --> 00:53:55,540
 Nema dobro loše,

1120
00:53:55,660 --> 00:53:56,960
 nego kontekst.

1121
00:53:56,960 --> 00:53:57,460
 Znači,

1122
00:53:57,460 --> 00:53:58,780
 ono što je u jednom kontekstu

1123
00:53:58,780 --> 00:53:59,100
 dobro,

1124
00:53:59,100 --> 00:54:00,080
 u drugim kontekstu loše.

1125
00:54:00,080 --> 00:54:01,480
 A netko uvijek sjedi na klupi.

1126
00:54:01,480 --> 00:54:02,320
 Da.

1127
00:54:02,320 --> 00:54:02,920
 I sad,

1128
00:54:02,920 --> 00:54:03,720
 samo je poanta

1129
00:54:03,720 --> 00:54:04,980
 koliko smo mi svjesni

1130
00:54:04,980 --> 00:54:07,160
 koju igru igramo,

1131
00:54:07,160 --> 00:54:08,780
 koju igru želimo igrati,

1132
00:54:08,780 --> 00:54:11,580
 gdje želimo biti na terenu,

1133
00:54:11,580 --> 00:54:11,960
 jel?

1134
00:54:11,960 --> 00:54:13,440
 I, kako je rekao,

1135
00:54:13,440 --> 00:54:15,120
 gdje možemo dati najbolje od sebe.

1136
00:54:15,120 --> 00:54:15,860
 U kojoj ligi.

1137
00:54:15,860 --> 00:54:16,280
 Da.

1138
00:54:16,280 --> 00:54:17,480
 Profesore,

1139
00:54:17,480 --> 00:54:18,180
 hvala vam lijepa.

1140
00:54:18,180 --> 00:54:18,960
 Hvala vama,

1141
00:54:18,960 --> 00:54:20,020
 hvala vašim gledateljima.

1142
00:54:20,020 --> 00:54:21,600
 Bio ovo još jedan podcast.

1143
00:54:21,600 --> 00:54:22,080
 Mrežnica,

1144
00:54:22,080 --> 00:54:23,820
 malo sad možemo svi zapravo

1145
00:54:23,820 --> 00:54:24,760
 razmisliti o tome

1146
00:54:24,760 --> 00:54:25,820
 koji i kakav film

1147
00:54:25,820 --> 00:54:27,040
 snimamo našeg života

1148
00:54:27,040 --> 00:54:27,800
 i što učiniti

1149
00:54:27,800 --> 00:54:28,540
 da nam taj film

1150
00:54:28,540 --> 00:54:29,220
 bude bolji

1151
00:54:29,220 --> 00:54:30,160
 i za nas gledaniji.

1152
00:54:30,160 --> 00:54:31,180
 Je sam to dobro rekla?

1153
00:54:31,180 --> 00:54:31,620
 Jest.

1154
00:54:31,840 --> 00:54:32,280
 Odlično.

1155
00:54:32,280 --> 00:54:33,060
 Hvala vam puno.

